Enter your guess: 40
Congratulations! You guessed the number in 5 attempts.
Do you want to play again? (yes/no): yes
Welcome to the Number Guessing Game ðŸ˜Š
Guess the number between 1 and 100.
Enter your guess: 60
Too low!
Enter your guess: 80
Too high!
Enter your guess: 70
Too low!
Enter your guess: 75
Too high!
Enter your guess: 73
You ran out of attempts. The number was 72.
Do you want to play again? (yes/no): no
Thanks for playing! You won 1 round(s).

        System.out.printf("Thanks for playing! You won %d round(s).\n", roundsWon);
        scanner.close();
    }
}
